title: Wholemeal Rye Bread
ingredients: ['320ml water', '2 tablespoons honey', '50g tablespoons butter, softened', '135g bread flour', '240g wholemeal flour', '50g rye flour', '1 1/2 tablespoons dried milk powder', '3 tablespoons dark brown soft sugar', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 teaspoons easy bake yeast', '60g Grape-Nuts cereal']
